title: Saudi's Sela Trading wraps up mega Ahly sponsorship deal - Egyptian Football
text:
Related Egypt's Ahly strike record sponsorship deal with Saudi Sela Trading Egyptian giants Ahly have signed a three-year, LE250 million sponsorship deal with Saudi Arabia’s Sela Trading Company to create the biggest sponsorship deal in Egyptian football history.
The Saudi corporation beat off competition from Al-Ahram Advertising Agency, Ahly’s sponsor for the past three years, to secure a three-year contract with Egypt’s most successful club.
Ahly held a press conference at the club's headquarters on Thursday to sign the contracts with the Saudi company, with club chairman Mahmoud Taher attendance.
